"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Donald Trump said that after the Iranian ship ignored warnings, the US navy damaged its engine room. The US has shown a video of the attack.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Navy Damages Iranian Ship\",            \"translated_version\": \"Donald Trump dijo que despu\u00e9s de que el barco iran\u00ed ignor\u00f3 las advertencias, la marina de EE.UU. da\u00f1\u00f3 su sala de motores. EE.UU. mostr\u00f3 un video del ataque.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Marina de EE.UU. Da\u00f1a Barco Iran\u00ed\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"An earthquake with a magnitude of 7.4 hit, according to the Japan Meteorological Agency.\",            \"english_title\": \"Earthquake in Japan\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un terremoto de magnitud 7.4 ocurri\u00f3, seg\u00fan la Agencia Meteorol\u00f3gica de Jap\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Terremoto en Jap\u00f3n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Authorities have suspended officers and are investigating their actions.\",            \"english_title\": \"Officers Suspended\",            \"translated_version\": \"Las autoridades han suspendido a los oficiales y est\u00e1n investigando sus acciones.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Oficiales Suspendidos\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The brand warned that eating the pur\u00e9es could be very dangerous.\",            \"english_title\": \"Dangerous Pur\u00e9es Warning\",            \"translated_version\": \"La marca advirti\u00f3 que comer los pur\u00e9s podr\u00eda ser muy peligroso.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Advertencia de Pur\u00e9s Peligrosos\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Energy markets have been unstable since the US and Israel attacked Iran on February 28.\",            \"english_title\": \"Unstable Energy Markets\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los mercados de energ\